#Time-Series-Forecasting and Temperature Analysis

##Project Overview
This project investigates different approaches to forecasting temperature time series data and compares their performance.

##Tools
- Microsoft Excel
- Statistical Analysis
- Time Series Forecasting

##Methods Applied
- Irwin anomaly detection method
- Moving Average
- Weighted Moving Average
- Exponential Smoothing
- Double Exponential Smoothing
- Triple Exponential Smoothing
- Adaptive Smoothing
- Holt-Winters Model
- Trend Modeling
- Correlation and Regression Analysis
- Seasonal Analysis
- Autoregression

##Results
The project compares forecasting accuracy across different methods and evaluates the impact of trend and seasonality on prediction quality.
